Meet <b>yumi222</b>, the new Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Residing at <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=yumi2222"><a href='/home/?user=yumi2222'>23017-C Bluebird Street</a> in Lakeview</a>, yumi222 has been a Millsberry citizen since August 14, 2007. <br><br>In the spirit of summer, yumi222 came to our attention as one of the top scorers on Kai's Ultimate Surfari. She also considers herself a very deep thinker, and finds a lot of peace in her thatched reed hut. <br><br>Yumi222 loves being outdoors, including camping in her own backyard, and being active&mdash;like going boxing, at home, in a room full of multi-colored heavy bags! While yumi222 is a little tough, she's also quite charming. She loves teddy bears, singing pop music, and organizing her seven trophies. <br><br>Yumi222 hopes to win even more gold, which is why you can find her playing away at the Arcade, downtown. If you're up for it, swing by and challenge her to a round while taking in her favorite tunes of drum 'n' bass and classic rock! <br></div>
